WRITING.TITLE: Final Fantasy VIII (8) is one of the best Final Fantasies
WRITING.TEXT: I think Final Fantasy VIII is one of the best games in the series. I would say "better than VII" but I don't know if that's necessarily true. But I do LIKE it better than VII. And I know that's enough to get beat up by fellow RPG fans. I like the realism of not only the graphics (the people look like people) but the plot itself is more believable to me as well.
